{"tid":493382,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵番一套戲睇，但唔記得名淨係記得少少情節","createTime":"2017-12-08T12:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T16:13:40.000Z","uid":18768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92c82cbddc225595c7e04c933d383723aa45a468","tid":493382,"uid":18768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"好似係講喪屍或病毒片。<br />\n<br />\n一班人逃走緊，入左underground tunnel，入面好多蜘蛛。<br />\n入左tunnel入一間房避一避。<br />\n<br />\n之後出番黎繼續走，途中有人被咬一啖。<br />\n<br />\n離開左tunnel被軍隊救，被咬個條友被軍人拖左去帳篷入面，佢就屍變比軍人開槍射死。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人記得咩戲？唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7227c02e5a149e2c064e4c89de3113bf39d3afc8","tid":493382,"uid":90749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:46:56.000Z","msg":"Cloverfield 末世凶煞"},{"pid":"701724bfdb3fd0d2cf86e8eb401f09e9338dd056","tid":493382,"uid":18768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cloverfield 末世凶煞</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}